messages.message: I've noticed on my new user creation within instabase.com (http://instabase.com) and dogfood that it required me to click resend email in order to get the email. Not sure if this is a known issue or if this is something just on my end

That happens to me too :slightly_smiling_face:
Over time I stopped minding because when I make a user for a prospect/customer, it doesn't send them an email right away. That way I can better control how they access the platform

Same. That’s why it’s good you mention it, Josh. It got normal already to me, too.
We should make sure it works for our customers in production.
